{
  "stem": "9156.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there was lots of homework being done, you know, putting things together in the home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And-- but those children lived very often with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There was really no room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I can't describe all this in detail.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There is a store.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There are two very small rooms, one of that is always dark, all day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The other one is light.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But the beds had to always be carried in the evening from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I'm only saying all this because it's important memories.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But I have to say, I also want to say it, that too many people think that all Jews were rich in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And in fact, I remember a Jewish refugee says, well, certainly, we were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I said, not we.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We never were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But this family had a lot of meaning to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So these are very early memories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "There are many others I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I-- maybe the things that I like to talk about are the things that have influenced my whole philosophy or thinking, even very young.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I was maybe, I don't know, maybe six years old or something like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Hannah was a little older, eight years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And Ruth was much younger, so I'm, I'm in preschool, I forgot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, to me, that's really exciting, that here's a baby, who is a Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And mother, who was Orthodox, if you want to, but not rigid ever, said, well, sure.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But only if you allow the two older girls to look at it and be there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here we were.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I admired my little sister, sitting in that crib so quietly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the angels around her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And afterwards they said, well, anybody wants to say some poems.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was a showoff, I guess, all my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
